Module cloud.piranha.cdi.weld
Package cloud.piranha.cdi.weld

Class RealtimeHttpServletRequestWrapper

java.lang.Object
cloud.piranha.cdi.weld.RealtimeHttpServletRequestWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
HttpServletRequest, ServletRequest
Direct Known Subclasses:
WeldHttpServletRequest
public abstract class RealtimeHttpServletRequestWrapper extends Object implements HttpServletRequest
An HttpServletRequest wrapper that consistently consults the getWrapped() method for every operation.
Author:
Arjan Tijms, Manfred Riem (mriem@manorrock.com)
